[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 2. Right Sidebar Bet Slip (Desktop)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Sidebar pattern**: 350px right sidebar with slide-in animation[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Integrated bet types**: Complete bet type selector within the bet slip[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Individual stake inputs**: For straight bets[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Combined stake inputs**: For parlay/teaser/if-bet[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Professional styling**: Navy gradient background with gold accents[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### 3. Mobile Bottom Sheet[m
