[32m+[m[32m## Key Features Implemented[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Bet Types with Real Functionality[m
[32m+[m[32m```typescript[m
[32m+[m[32m// Straight: Individual stake per bet[m
[32m+[m[32m// Parlay: Combined stake with multiplied odds[m
[32m+[m[32m// Teaser: Adjusted odds (70% of original) for better spreads[m
[32m+[m[32m// If-Bet: Conditional betting where second bet depends on first[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Body Class Management[m
[32m+[m[32m```css[m
[32m+[m[32mbody.bet-slip-mode {[m
[32m+[m[32m  margin-right: 350px; /* Desktop layout adjustment */[m
[32m+[m[32m  transition: margin-right 0.3s ease-in-out;[m
[32m+[m[32m}[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
